Dedicated Turn Lanes adds an intersection tool for building generated dedicated turn lane segments on incoming roads. Hover an intersection to preview eligible approaches, then apply the split and road replacement in one workflow. The tool looks for compatible same-width road prefabs and uses angle-aware spacing to handle skewed intersections more reliably.
